	<h1 class="title">换了新总裁，那个放纪录片的探索频道打算卷土重来</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Brooks Barnes, John Koblin</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-07 08:50:20 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20215/medium/20215.png?1451909349" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


